      "content": "wait r u serious? hydrogen peroxide? i read online that you shouldn't put anything in your ear if the eardrum might be damaged. is it really safe to just pour that in there? i'm kinda scared i broke something. if i do the peroxide thing, will it actually fix the hearing loss or is that just for the wax?",
